---
title: Cal Smart Zesty Apricot-Glazed Pork Chops with Golden Bulgur and Garden Salad
description: Sweet and sticky apricot pulls double duty with a savoury glaze and a standout dressing in this dish. If you're looking for a dinner salad that is jam-packed with flavour, this is it!
